bodybuilding macho stuff.

127
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,300
I'm gonna create a whole
new style just for this gig.

128
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:17,067
Yes, he won't know what hit him.

129
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:17,900
- I don't know.

130
00:07:17,933 --> 00:07:20,033
I don't like the
sounds of this guy.

131
