234
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,700
- Yeah, absolutely.

235
00:12:38,733 --> 00:12:41,433
- Yeah, I'm here now.

236
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:43,667
Yeah.

237
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:46,233
